  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://athomewithgrowingold.com/wp-content/uploads/home-slides-081.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/shetuan/d3d43ba6-d560-405d-9496-e4d71e824f7d.jpg\" />&nbsp;</span></a><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tRest<br />\n\tRest means not at work. What or who is resting? How is the action done? Where does the action take place?</p>\n<p>\n\tThis week's topic: They were resting... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) rest at home<br />\n\t2) rest at a resort<br />\n\t3) take a short rest when hiking<br />\n\t4) rest for a short period of time<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tNot too long ago, Sean found his things were displaced; they were not where they were supposed to be. Although the changes were ever so slight, Sean still caught onto it. At first, he just thought maybe he moved those things himself and just forgot about it. When it kept happening time and again, Sean started to get the feeling someone might be looking through his things. That was such a ridiculous idea at the time, that just to be able to put his mind at rest, Sean decided to install a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/surveillance\" target=\"_blank\">surveillance</a> camera in his own office.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710234091945/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912810/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912810\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p979868/\">四六级终要停考？将被国家英语能力等级考试取代！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p965825/\">2016年度评价最高的12门课</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p977129/\">双语美文：最好的圣诞礼物</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p977132/\">任何地方的笔印都能擦掉？到底怎么做？！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p981224/\">中国90后富豪榜：拼不过爹，也拼不过脸……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p930439/\">英语学习推荐：听说读写全面提升的法宝</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p981261/\">做一个会20种语言的小鲜肉是怎样一种体验？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p756246/\">新概念英语的正确打开方式</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p970185/\">《生活大爆炸》笔记S10E8：宝贝计划</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p884089/\">雅思听力中不可不知的逻辑关系</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
